{"tid":336098,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"Unlight:SchizoChronicle-對戰卡牌","createTime":"2017-07-26T06:44:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T17:45:01.000Z","uid":115718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5b6fecc5e2be6ef14df675ca51d030cee9175410","tid":336098,"uid":115718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://blog.files.qoo-app.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/17072508313592.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.files.qoo-app.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F17072508313592.jpg&h=bffd6743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本 Techway 旗下哥特風手機遊戲《Unlight:SchizoChronicle（アンライト：スキゾクロニクル）》Android 版今日（7月26日）已正式配信，QooApp 提供下載！iOS 版尚未公佈配信時間，相信不會太久。(本文系QooApp獨家原創，如欲轉載，請註明出處 <a href=\"http://www.qoo-app.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.qoo-app.com&d=R39rRjhGqRHJV8Ki76lo2kjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=f8d4785b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.qoo-app.com</a>) #5712<br />\n<br />\n《Unlight:SchizoChronicle》是一款實施對戰卡牌遊戲。玩家需在和 Unlight 似是而非的世界中，通過討伐怪物，蒐集「混沌碎片」，解開世界的秘密。由於本作玩法複雜，正式配信版也比內測版新增了教學環節，第一次打開遊戲的玩家請務必仔細閱讀。(本文系QooApp獨家原創，如欲轉載，請註明出處 <a href=\"http://www.qoo-app.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.qoo-app.com&d=R39rRjhGqRHJV8Ki76lo2kjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=f8d4785b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.qoo-app.com</a>) #4834<br />\n<br />\n本次卡面、技能圖全部經過重新繪製，非常令人耳目一新！官方公告表明8月會新增卡片分解合成、每日獎勵、記錄等功能，地圖任務、劇情故事、玩家換裝等功能也會在將來實裝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://blog.files.qoo-app.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/17072603155522.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.files.qoo-app.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F17072603155522.jpg&h=d0b732f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://blog.files.qoo-app.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/17072603162890.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.files.qoo-app.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F201